{
  "texts": [
    "Briefly, plugs of pathogen were taken out of liquid nitrogen 3 weeks before the experiment, dried, and placed on V8 agar.",
    "Plates were placed in the dark at 27 °C.",
    "1.5 weeks before the experiment, pathogen cultures were sub-cultured onto new V8 plates.",
    "Finally, 2 days before the experiment, P. palmivora plates were once again sub-cultured to create 120 thin (10 mL) V8 agar plates.",
    "Plates were then incubated in the dark at 27 °C until the day of the experiment.Prior to inoculation, 2 leaves from each plant were selected for inoculation based on size, health, and developmental stage."
  ]
}